Module net.etf.project
Package net.etf.project.statistics

Class DailyReport

java.lang.Object
net.etf.project.statistics.DailyReport
public class DailyReport extends Object
The DailyReport class represents a summary of financial and operational metrics for a particular day. It aggregates data from all the receipts for that day and calculates important statistics like income, discounts, promotions, repair costs, and more.
